[0.3.7]
* Add Cloudron `ldap` addon support
* Add optional LDAP authentication middleware (`LDAP_AUTH_ENABLED=true`) using Cloudron LDAP credentials
* Keep static Basic auth only as fallback when LDAP auth is disabled

[0.3.6]
* Add optional HTTP Basic authentication middleware (`BASIC_AUTH_USERNAME` + `BASIC_AUTH_PASSWORD`)
* Protect all routes except `/health` when Basic auth is enabled

[0.3.5]
* Enable Cloudron `optionalSso` in manifest so SSO mode can be activated on install/update
* Remove proxyAuth addon (rollback to app-level auth)

[Older versions removed proxyAuth entries]

[0.3.1]
* Initial release
